definitions.definition: Dried corn ( maize ) milled ( ground ) to a meal , especially a coarse one.
examples: She made a kind of polenta from cornmeal and chicken broth, with some cheese sprinkled on top.

definitions.definition: Any cereal grain meal or flour .

main_definition: Dried corn ( maize ) milled ( ground ) to a meal , especially a coarse one.
secondary_definitions: ( archaic , especially before 18th c. ) Any cereal grain meal or flour .
